OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Jack
OL,4,CGledhill
OL,6,FJack Gledhill, Age: 100, Royal
OL,7,FEngineers
OL,9,FInterviewed 21 February 2024
OL,11,FAn apprentice patternmaker who joined
OL,12,Fthe Royal Engineers and trained as a
OL,13,FSapper, Mr Gledhill was put on an
OL,14,Finstructor's course.
OL,16,FHe then trained many troops in the
OL,17,Flead-up to D-Day in how to avoid enemy
OL,18,Fmines, booby traps and obstacles,
OL,19,Fbuild bridges on land and sea and use
OL,20,Fropes for heavy lifting.
