OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Jack
OL,4,CGledhill
OL,6,FThe only way he could get into the
OL,7,Fservices originally was to sign as a
OL,8,Fregular.
OL,10,FHe was sent on a six-week initial
OL,11,Ftraining course, and then went on to
OL,12,Ftrain as a Royal Engineer sapper.
OL,14,F"They kept me behind to put me on an
OL,15,Finstructor's course to train
OL,16,Frecruits," he said.
OL,18,F"I passed it and they kept me behind
OL,19,Fand trained sapper recruits."
