OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Jack
OL,4,CGledhill
OL,6,FJack is sure that many of those
OL,7,Frecruits went to Normandy.
OL,9,FIdentified on landing by white bands
OL,10,Faround their helmets, Royal Engineers
OL,11,Fhelped design, build and put together
OL,12,Fthe Mulberry artificial harbour and
OL,13,Fclear lanes and establish exits on the
OL,14,Fbeaches.
OL,16,FTheir tasks also included removing
OL,17,Fvehicles that had become stuck and
OL,18,Falso clearing obstacles such as mines.
OL,20,FThis work on D-Day often had to be
OL,21,Fdone while the men came under fire.
