OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Jack
OL,4,CGledhill
OL,6,FMr Gledhill said: "I missed out.
OL,8,F"Instead of going with them to be put
OL,9,Fin units they kept me behind and I
OL,10,Ffelt that, like I hadn't gone. I had
OL,11,Fto accept it.
OL,13,F"A sapper does a lot of work.
OL,15,F"He deals with booby traps, bridges on
OL,16,Fwater and on land, we used to train
OL,17,Fthem to build that. And ropes for
OL,18,Flifting stuff about - we had to train
OL,19,Ffor all of that."
