OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Jack
OL,4,CGledhill
OL,6,FAlthough Mr Gledhill regrets missing
OL,7,Fout on the invasion, Royal Engineers
OL,8,Fwere among the best-trained troops in
OL,9,Fthe British Army and that expertise
OL,10,Fwas instrumental in the success of D-
OL,11,FDay.
